             was indicted for <rs id="t17960406-13-off74" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960406-13-off74" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-13-off74" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17960406-13-cd75" type="crimeDate">31st of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960406-13-off74 t17960406-13-cd75"></join>, four linen shirts, value 4s. a nankeen jacket, value 6d. a linen pin-a-sore, value 6d. nine linen clonts, value 5s. four pair of stockings, value 3s. a calico bed-gown, value 6d. a dimity petticoat, value 2s. and a linen pillow case, value 1d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17960406-13-victim159" type="victimName">
